\n希伯來文：優秀民族猶太佬既語言<br />\n<br />\nFF得黎太大貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果我細個開始學語言就好，畀老母帶去學埋啲垃圾珠心算浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家年紀大左學習能力有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細佬仔係讀書既黃金時間，因為腦部結構未成班，神經細胞仲急速生長緊，而記憶就係以神經細胞既形式儲存 （synaptic plasticity）<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候學外語，真係學哂英德法意西俄都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335502f124cc9120b77c830ed9ae7a8059c1443e","tid":158329,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日韓德法西意俄<br />\n拉丁 希臘 梵語<br />\n希伯來 阿拉伯</blockquote><br />\n真係全部識? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打目標同我極相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想咋<br />\n<br />\n日韓雙修中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e706eb79179c670aac9da0dca1f3ead5cc1c817e","tid":158329,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>流利粵普英，識少少手語、德文同法文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但香港地學外文真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最少都千千聲</blockquote><br />\n而且無學外語既環境，學得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9533dce4d3a5ac5a372653eaa24f74914cb3f7","tid":158329,"uid":5436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"廣東話,英文,國語極垃圾<br />\n學緊日文德文"},{"pid":"632ce0361911bcd148e5acb7f458754698fb2af9","tid":158329,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d243224f7f822e6a4451d3a2b124059fbff88be","tid":158329,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每樣想學既語言都有啲